query:
SELECT 
  wz.id as zoneId,
  wz.code as zoneCode,
  wz.name as zoneName,
  COUNT(DISTINCT wl.id) as totalLocations,
  COUNT(DISTINCT i.id) as totalInventoryRecords,
  SUM(i.quantity) as totalQuantity,
  SUM(i.reservedQuantity) as totalReserved
FROM warehouseZones wz
LEFT JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON wl.zoneId = wz.id
LEFT JOIN inventory i ON i.locationId = wl.id
WHERE wz.code = 'EXP'
GROUP BY wz.id, wz.code, wz.name;
